    <item>
      <title>印度或调整规则以控制债券指数的热门流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/india-may-tweak-rules-to-check-hot-flows-on-bond-index-entry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部高级官员表示，如果大量资金流入引发波动，印度可能会修改发行有资格在全球指数中交易的新债券的规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/india-may-tweak-rules-to-check-hot-flows-on-bond-index-entry</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:12:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度政府计划稳步降低债务率至 50%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/india-s-government-plans-to-steadily-lower-debt-ratio-to-50</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，印度政府计划在未来几年内将债务率降至国内生产总值的50%左右，并维持在这一水平左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/india-s-government-plans-to-steadily-lower-debt-ratio-to-50</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
